title: City Beneath The Sea (1971)
description: A group of 21st-century colonists inhabit an underwater city called Pacifica. Originally intended as a purely scientific installation, the U. S. government wants to stash all its gold reserves from Fort Knox there, along with a fantastic new radioactive element. The brother of Pacifica&#039;s returning former commander plans to steal the gold and on top of that, the city faces destruction by an asteroid from outer space.
